author: Jayne Yutig
title: San Diego Restaurant Week returns this weekend Sept. 22-Sept. 29 | cbs8.com
text:
SAN DIEGO — San Diego County's favorite culinary event is back this weekend starting Sept. 22 through Sept. 29.
'Fall into Flavor' Presented by the California Restaurant Association, San Diego Restaurant week highlights more than 100 restaurants across the county, from Oceanside to Chula Vista.
For eight days, diners can visit dozens of restaurants and taste dishes from curated multi-course menus. Participating restaurants will offer lunch and dinner menus at varying prices.
Reservations are highly recommended.
To start planning your brunch or night out, click here.
